# PlantMD Terms of Service

## 1. Acceptance of Terms
By downloading, installing, or using PlantMD ("the App"), you agree to be bound by these Terms of Service ("Terms"). If you do not agree to these Terms, do not use the App.

## 2. Description of Service
PlantMD is a mobile application that provides AI-powered plant disease diagnosis, care recommendations, and plant management tools. The App offers both free and premium subscription features.

## 3. Subscription Terms

> - PlantMD offers premium features through paid subscriptions, which may be billed on a monthly, annual, or other recurring basis.  
> - Subscription prices, terms, and trial offers may vary by location and may change from time to time.  
> - The current price and offer details will be clearly displayed at the time of purchase in the App.  
> - Subscriptions automatically renew unless cancelled at least 24 hours before the end of the current period.  
> - Payment will be charged to your Apple ID account at confirmation of purchase.  
> - You can manage and cancel your subscription through your Apple ID Account Settings.

## 4. User Responsibilities
You agree to use the App responsibly and not to misuse our services. The plant care advice provided is for informational purposes only and should not replace professional horticultural consultation for valuable or irreplaceable plants.

## 5. Limitation of Liability
PlantMD and its developers are not liable for any plant damage, loss, or death that may result from following the App's recommendations. Plant care involves many variables beyond our AI's analysis.

## 6. Privacy
Your privacy is important to us. Please review our [Privacy Policy](privacy.html) to understand how we collect, use, and protect your information.

## 7. Changes to Terms
We reserve the right to modify these Terms at any time. Continued use of the App after changes constitutes acceptance of the new Terms.

## 8. Contact Information
